<!-- wp:heading {"align":"wide","textColor":"accent"} -->
<h2 class="alignwide has-accent-color has-text-color">Abstract</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column {"width":"100%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:100%"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Deep Learning has found great success in the field of image processing and computer vision and has acquired immense research attention in recent years. Object Detection and Recognition has found wide-ranging applications in traffic control, human-computer interaction, digital forensics, gesture recognition, augmented reality and visual surveillance. The use of Deep Learning in object detection has enabled the learning of deeper features and can address the problems existing in traditional architectures. To acquaint the learners with theoretical and practical knowledge of Object Detection &amp; Recognition, and its interesting applications, a five-day workshop has been arranged by Deep Learning Lab, NCAI and SEECS. The workshop will help the participants get a deep dive into the underlying architecture and algorithms used for Object Detection and Recognition and get hands-on experience with the training of deep learning models. Become a part of this exciting workshop and learn about the interesting applications of Object Detection and Recognition using Deep Learning through enlightening lectures and training classes.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"wide","textColor":"accent"} -->
<h2 class="alignwide has-accent-color has-text-color">Learning Outcomes</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column {"width":"100%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:100%"><!-- wp:group -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The workshop will give a knowledge boost around following points:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol><li>Introduction to Machine Learning and object detection applications&nbsp;</li><li>Object Detection vs Object Recognition</li><li>Implementation algorithms for Object Detection</li><li>Implementation algorithms for Object Recognition</li></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"wide","textColor":"accent"} -->
<h2 class="alignwide has-accent-color has-text-color">Key Benefits</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:columns {"align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide"><!-- wp:column {"width":"100%"} -->
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:100%"><!-- wp:group -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>After attending the workshop, you will be able to:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol><li>Have a better understanding of Object Detection and Recognition systems&nbsp;</li><li>Identify the key challenges related to Object Detection and Recognition</li><li>Identify the key application areas of Object Detection and Recognition</li></ol>
<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
